<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>DHCP.io - Free Dynamic DNS</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="text-align: center;"><h1>DHCP.io - Free Dynamic DNS</h1></div>

    <table width="100%">
      <tr><td width="15%" valign="top">
        </td>
        <td width="60%" valign="top">
          <p>DHCP.io allows you to control the DNS entry belonging to a name beneath the <tt>.dhcp.io</tt> domain.</p>
          <p>For example you could configure the name <tt>steve.dhcp.io</tt> to point to the IP of your home gateway.</p>
        </td>
        <td width="25%" valign="top">
          <h2>User Menu</h2>
          <form method="POST" action="/cgi-bin/index.cgi">
            <input type="hidden" name="mode" value="login">
            <table>
              <tr><td>Username</td>
                <td> <input type="text" name="lname"></td>
              </tr>
              <tr><td>Password</td>
                <td> <input type="password" name="lpass"></td>
              </tr>
              <tr><td></td><td align="right"><input type="submit" name="submit" value="Login"></td></tr>
            </table>
          </form>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
